{"id":3425,"date":"2023-08-23T17:21:44","date_gmt":"2023-08-23T10:21:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/?p=3425"},"modified":"2023-10-12T16:54:12","modified_gmt":"2023-10-12T09:54:12","slug":"thong-tin-chi-tiet-ve-du-hoc-dai-loan-he-ngon-ngu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/thong-tin-chi-tiet-ve-du-hoc-dai-loan-he-ngon-ngu\/","title":{"rendered":"Th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>I. Du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Loan l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng Trung Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e0i Loan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn du h\u1ecdc. Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan, sinh vi\u00ean s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi ti\u1ebfng Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e2ng cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3428\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3428\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3428\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1692785952.jpg\" alt=\"du-hoc-dai-loan-he-ngon-ngu\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1692785952.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1692785952-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3428\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh, do \u0111\u00f3 sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn h\u1ecdc c\u00e1c kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 tin ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 ti\u1ebfng Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c n\u1eafm v\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng Trung Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap sinh vi\u00ean t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho vi\u1ec7c giao ti\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>II. \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c, <strong>du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/strong> c\u0169ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u du h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef. D\u1ef1a v\u00e0o tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>H\u1ecdc v\u1ea5n:<\/strong> T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT\/ Trung c\u1ea5p\/ Cao \u0111\u1eb3ng\/ \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc v\u1edbi GPA 6.0\/10\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef:<\/strong> TOCFL c\u1ea5p 1\/ TOEIC 300\/ IELTS 2.5 tr\u1edf l\u00ean<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3429\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3429\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3429\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/14-1692785952.jpg\" alt=\"dieu-kien\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/14-1692785952.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/14-1692785952-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3429\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u00f9y v\u00e0o tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 hoa ng\u1eef hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia c\u00e1c l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>&gt;&gt; XEM TH\u00caM:<\/strong> <a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/di-du-hoc-dai-loan-can-bao-nhieu-tien\/\">\u0110i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>III. C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi b\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du h\u1ecdc su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u00e0i Loan cung c\u1ea5p ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef. Xem x\u00e9t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp. Xem x\u00e9t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o, nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m IELTS ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p trung h\u1ecdc ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Thu th\u1eadp th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 chi ph\u00ed:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chi ph\u00ed h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed v\u00e0 c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y \u1edf \u0110\u00e0i Loan. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n cho sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3430\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3430\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3430\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/13-1692785952.jpg\" alt=\"thu-thap-thong-tin-ve-chi-phi\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/13-1692785952.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/13-1692785952-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3430\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Thu th\u1eadp th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 chi ph\u00ed<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd v\u00e0 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 Thu th\u1eadp v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd quan tr\u1ecdng, bao g\u1ed3m h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu, th\u1ebb sinh vi\u00ean, b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p, b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec3m, gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn ti\u1ebfng Anh (IELTS ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng), th\u01b0 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1eeb gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao ch\u00e9p v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 qu\u00e1n \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Visa du h\u1ecdc:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, sinh vi\u00ean c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c xin visa du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, visa du h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1eb7t ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u1ed7 \u1edf:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u1ed7 h\u1ecdc. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc, l\u1ecbch h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan kh\u00e1c. T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ed7 \u1edf, nh\u01b0 k\u00fd t\u00fac x\u00e1 sinh vi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c nh\u00e0 tr\u1ecd. X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u1ed7 \u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1ec1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 phong t\u1ee5c \u0110\u00e0i Loan \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 quy t\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, bao g\u1ed3m quy \u0111\u1ecbnh visa, lu\u1eadt lao \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 quy t\u1eafc k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3431\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3431\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3431\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/15-1692785952.jpg\" alt=\"tim-hieu-ve-van-hoa-va-quy-dinh-dia-phuong\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/15-1692785952.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/15-1692785952-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3431\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho vi\u1ec7c du h\u1ecdc, bao g\u1ed3m h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed, chi ph\u00ed sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, chi ph\u00ed \u0103n \u1edf v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c. T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng, vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m b\u00e1n th\u1eddi gian ho\u1eb7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>&gt;&gt; XEM TH\u00caM:<\/strong> <a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/chi-phi-du-hoc-dai-loan-he-ngon-ngu\/\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>IV. Top tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc n\u00ean h\u1ecdc khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc uy t\u00edn m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ba tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u00e0i Loan (National Taiwan University &#8211; NTU):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> L\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Loan, NTU \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng cao tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c, bao g\u1ed3m khoa h\u1ecdc t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kinh t\u1ebf, khoa h\u1ecdc x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt. NTU cung c\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng Trung Qu\u1ed1c cho sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Tsing Hua (National Tsing Hua University &#8211; NTHU):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> NTHU l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc danh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong c\u00e1c l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c khoa h\u1ecdc, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng tin, kinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd. NTHU c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u00e0nh cho sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3432\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3432\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3432\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/16-1692785952.jpg\" alt=\"National-Tsing-Hua-University\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/16-1692785952.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/16-1692785952-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3432\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>National Tsing Hua University<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Cheng Kung (National Cheng Kung University &#8211; NCKU):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> NCKU l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc danh ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc. NCKU c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c nhau trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c kinh t\u1ebf, qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng Trung Qu\u1ed1c cho sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ba trong s\u1ed1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc uy t\u00edn t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u00f4i khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb b\u1ea1n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1ec1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd, c\u01a1 s\u1edf v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef. H\u00e3y c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Smart Way s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea1n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3433\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3433\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3433\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17-1692785952.jpg\" alt=\"du-hoc-smart-way\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17-1692785952.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17-1692785952-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3433\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Du h\u1ecdc Smart Way<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngay h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/\">Smart Way<\/a>. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Fanpage:\u00a0<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/duhocsmartway\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Du h\u1ecdc Smart Way<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Email:<\/strong>\u00a0duhocsmartway@gmail.com<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hotline:\u00a0<\/strong>0983.741.042 \u2013 0988.108.164<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9:\u00a0<\/strong>S\u1ed1 27, li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 12, Khu \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb V\u0103n Kh\u00ea, Ph\u01b0\u1eddng La Kh\u00ea, Qu\u1eadn H\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng, Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>I. Du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan h\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef l\u00e0 g\u00ec? H\u1ec7 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Loan l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng Trung Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e0i Loan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn du h\u1ecdc. Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan, &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":3434,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[8],"tags":[11,50,12],"class_list":["post-3425","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-cam-nang-du-hoc","tag-du-hoc-dai-loan","tag-du-hoc-dai-loan-he-ngon-ngu","tag-he-ngon-ngu"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3425","targetHi